reviewText: Just okay, as travel videos go.  It does take you to some out of the way places in Mexico, but doesn't give you a well-rounded picture of the territorial and cultural variety that exists in this large, storied country.  You feel instead as if you are hopping here, there, and everywhere with no real plan in mind.  Okay for a single viewing, but not one I'd want to see over and over, and not one to pick if you can only pick one video to get a brief but comprehensive look at  the country of Mexico and its people.
